"Emacs defaults =custom-file= to =init.el=, but here =init.el= is a read-only "
"symlink into the Nix store, so anything Customize tries to persist would "
"fail to write. Stateful files like this must live outside Nix management to "
"stay mutable: point =custom-file= at a writable path under "
"=user-emacs-directory= (the directory itself is writable; only the symlinked "
"files are not) and load it so the saved values take effect."
