#. type: heading *
#: modules/configuration.org:2903
#, no-wrap
msgid "Speech to Text"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: modules/configuration.org:2905
#, no-wrap
msgid "Handy"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:2907
msgid ""
"[[https://handy.computer][Handy]] is an offline speech-to-text app: press a "
"hotkey, speak, and the transcription is typed into the focused field. The "
"binary is in nixpkgs (=pkgs.handy=, Linux and macOS), but neither nixpkgs "
"nor home-manager ships a module, and the upstream flake's own modules are "
"thin and Linux-only. So I wrote my own, driven from one switch across every "
"desktop."
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:2913
msgid ""
"Almost everything is per-user and cross-platform, so it lives in a "
"home-manager module: the package plus an autostart agent, a systemd user "
"service on Linux and a launchd agent on macOS. Each platform's block is "
"guarded with =mkIf= so it only references options that exist there, and to "
"avoid an attribute-name-versus-=pkgs= evaluation cycle under "
"=useGlobalPkgs=."
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:2919
msgid ""
"The one piece home-manager cannot express is system-level. Handy reads its "
"global hotkey straight from =/dev/input/event*= via evdev, which only the "
"=input= group may read, and group membership is a NixOS setting. So a thin "
"=flake.modules.nixos.handy= adds the user to that group, sharing the "
"=my.programs.handy.enable= switch with the home module. (=/dev/uinput=, used "
"to type the result back, is already granted to the session user by uaccess, "
"so no udev rule is needed.) macOS has no evdev and no group to join; there "
"the hotkey and microphone need Accessibility and Microphone permissions, "
"granted once by hand, since TCC has no declarative path."
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:2929
msgid ""
"The desktop profile enables it by default, setting the home switch on every "
"desktop and, on NixOS only, adding the =input= group through its =nixos= "
"block."
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:2938
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{ ... }:\n"
"let\n"
"  homeModule =\n"
"    {\n"
"      config,\n"
"      lib,\n"
"      pkgs,\n"
"      ...\n"
"    }:\n"
"    let\n"
"      cfg = config.my.programs.handy;\n"
"    in\n"
"    {\n"
"      options.my.programs.handy = {\n"
"        enable = lib.mkEnableOption \"Handy offline speech-to-text\";\n"
"        autostart = lib.mkOption {\n"
"          type = lib.types.bool;\n"
"          default = true;\n"
"          description = \"Start Handy on login.\";\n"
"        };\n"
"      };"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:2960
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"config = lib.mkIf cfg.enable (\n"
"  lib.mkMerge [\n"
"    { home.packages = [ pkgs.handy ]; }"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:2964
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(lib.mkIf pkgs.stdenv.hostPlatform.isLinux {\n"
"  systemd.user.services.handy = lib.mkIf cfg.autostart {\n"
"    Unit = {\n"
"      Description = \"Handy speech-to-text\";\n"
"      PartOf = [ \"graphical-session.target\" ];\n"
"      After = [ \"graphical-session.target\" ];\n"
"    };\n"
"    Service = {\n"
"      ExecStart = lib.getExe pkgs.handy;\n"
"      Restart = \"on-failure\";\n"
"      RestartSec = 5;\n"
"    };\n"
"    Install.WantedBy = [ \"graphical-session.target\" ];\n"
"  };\n"
"})"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:2980
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"      (lib.mkIf pkgs.stdenv.hostPlatform.isDarwin {\n"
"        launchd.agents.handy = lib.mkIf cfg.autostart {\n"
"          enable = true;\n"
"          config = {\n"
"            ProgramArguments = [ (lib.getExe pkgs.handy) ];\n"
"            RunAtLoad = true;\n"
"            KeepAlive.SuccessfulExit = false;\n"
"          };\n"
"        };\n"
"      })\n"
"    ]\n"
"  );\n"
"};"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:2996
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"nixosModule =\n"
"  {\n"
"    config,\n"
"    lib,\n"
"    ...\n"
"  }:\n"
"  {\n"
"    options.my.programs.handy.enable = lib.mkEnableOption \"Handy offline "
"speech-to-text\";"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:3005
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"      config = lib.mkIf config.my.programs.handy.enable {\n"
"        users.users.${config.my.username}.extraGroups = [ \"input\" ];\n"
"      };\n"
"    };\n"
"in\n"
"{\n"
"  flake.modules.homeManager.handy = homeModule;\n"
"  flake.modules.nixos.handy = nixosModule;\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

